   Site Search

   Welcome to our collection of photos related to oil spills and other
   hazardous materials topics. To find photos, choose a photo topic
   keyword from our keyword lists:
     * A - M keywords
     * N - Z keywords

Using the Photos

   You can save any photo in either JPEG format (best for most projects)
   or high-resolution format (best for high-quality publishing).

   You're free to copy and use the photos in this collection; they are not
   copyrighted. We request that you credit us when you use our materials
   in your publications.

To Learn More

   To learn more about an incident depicted in a photo, check our Response
   Reports and Case Histories.

